  ('medical-tech-moex-06868', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關mef基因在Macrolide-Lincosamide-Streptogramin B抗藥的⾓⾊，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["對macrolide具抗性，但對lincosamide和streptogramin B具感受性", "帶有mef基因的鏈球菌呈現M表現型", "主要由23S rRNA domain V甲基化所致", "mefA與mefE序列相似度⾼達90%"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9bfd57b3ecc5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c91d6115277c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 49, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06869', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關細菌ribotyping（核糖體基因分型）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["屬於RFLP（Restriction fragment length polymorphism）分析應⽤之⼀種", "針對5S及16S rRNA，並不包括23S rRNA", "細菌具有多套rRNA基因拷⾙數⽬，有利分型", "需使⽤探針雜交"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9bfd57b3ecc5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c91d6115277c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06870', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '為釐清病⼈近期是否感染parvovirus B19，下列何種檢測是最適當的？', '["偵測⾎清中的IgG抗體", "分離純化出⾎清中的病毒", "⽤RT-PCR偵測⾎清中的病毒核酸RNA", "⽤PCR偵測⾎清中的病毒核酸DNA"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9bfd57b3ecc5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c91d6115277c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 51, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06871', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於疱疹病毒科（Herpesviridae）感染的分⼦鑑定，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["有分⼦檢測法，可同時偵測、區分HSV-1與HSV-2", "有分⼦檢測法，檢測VZV（Varicella-zoster virus）時，可以區分野⽣型與疫苗株", "若檢測出⼈類疱疹病毒第六型（Human herpesvirus-6），即證實此病毒是引起病⼈病徵的病原，因為此病 毒在⼀般⼈並不存在", "若檢測出⼈類疱疹病毒第七型（Human herpesvirus-7），並無法證實此病毒是引起病⼈病徵的病原，因為 此病毒在⼈群中廣泛存在"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9bfd57b3ecc5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c91d6115277c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 52, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-06872', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-108-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於唐⽒症之敘述，何者錯誤？', '["通常在懷孕第14～20週進⾏唐⽒症產前⺟⾎篩檢", "篩檢結果為⾼危險群的孕婦，可抽⽺⽔分析第21號染⾊體", "檢測結果只有⼆條第21號染⾊體，就沒有罹患唐⽒症的疑慮", "⽤STR標誌分析染⾊體個數時，可選⽤四核苷酸重複（tetranucleotide repeats）的STR markers"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9bfd57b3ecc5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c91d6115277c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108030", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師、職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 53, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
